title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2012-2014 Chevy Camaro 3.6L
description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N air intake on your 2012 to 2014 Chevy Camaro 3.6L.

K&N 57-3078 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2012 to 2014 Chevy Camaro with a 3.6L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 13.14 horsepower at 5100 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 57-3078 also includes a rotomolded polyethylene intake tube with a custom heat shield designed to increase air flow and isolate intake air from engine heat.
tags: K&N Cold Air Intake, Chevy Camaro, Chevrolet, how to install, k&n air intake for chevy camaro K&N air intake
